These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: rock, indie, country, reggae, r&b
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: iris, lily, rose, amaryllis, azalea
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, davidoff, montecristo, bolivar, alhambra
The people have 5 different jobs:  pilot, coach, photographer, police-officer, manager
 1. the manager is on the right of the photographer##1
 2. the person who growsrose is on the left of the fan indie##1
 3. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the pilot##1
 4. the fan country is the fan country##1
 5. the pilot is the person who growsiris##1
 6. the fan r&b is on the left of the fan country##1
 7. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
 8. the fan reggae is on the right of the police-officer##1
 9. the fan reggae is on the far right##1
10. the fan rock is on the left of the photographer##1
11. the fan r&b is between the davidoff-smoker and the person who growsazalea##2
12. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the person who growslily##1
13. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the fan country##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Music-Genre      | rock        | indie | r&b     | country   | reggae |
| Flower   | rose     | lily      | amaryllis | azalea   | iris    |
| Cigar   | bolivar  | davidoff     | bongani | montecristo | alhambra  |
| Job           | coach | photographer      | manager     | police-officer   | pilot     |

