.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  freelancer, pilot, analyst, coach, librarian
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: crime, horror, musical, satire, family
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: july, june, february, october, september
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: daffodil, bellflower, balloon-flower, tulip, poppy
 1. the person who growspoppy is in the middle##1
 2. the person watching family movies is on the left of the freelancer##1
 3. the pilot is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
 4. the librarian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 5. the person who growsbellflower is between the person who's birthday is in july and the person watching family movies##2
 6. the person who growstulip is the pilot##1
 7. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in february is the person watching satire movies##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the pilot##1
10. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
11. the person who's birthday is in february is the analyst##1
12. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Job         | coach | freelancer | librarian    | pilot  | analyst    |
| Movie-Genre   | family    | horror       | musical      | crime | satire        |
| Birthday   | september   | june     | july    | october  | february     |
| Flower     | balloon-flower    | bellflower | poppy | tulip | daffodil |

