.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  lawyer, mechanic, photographer, pilot, writer
The people use 5 different means of transport: tram, van, helicopter, bike, scooter
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: january, march, february, april, december
City: edinburgh, prague, new-york, miami, hannover
 1. the writer is the person who's birthday is in march##1
 2. the person traveling to miami is in the middle##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in april is in the middle##1
 4. the person driving the tram is in the middle##1
 5. the writer is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
 6. the mechanic is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
 8. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left##1
10. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person driving the bike##1
11. the photographer is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
12. the pilot is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
13. the person traveling to hannover is between the person driving the scooter and the photographer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Job         | lawyer | writer     | photographer   | mechanic   | pilot |
| Transport   | scooter  | van | tram | bike | helicopter        |
| Birthday   | february      | march      | april       | december       | january       |
| City         | prague | hannover  | miami    | edinburgh    | new-york        |

