.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-4::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: family, fantasy, animation, adventure, zombie
There are 5 different favourite beverages: water, tea, iced-tea, lemonade, milk
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, tram, motorbike, bus, skateboard
5 different games are played: whist, snooker, backgammon, mah-jongg, chess
 1. the person playing snooker is on the far left##1
 2. the person drinking water is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
 4. the person playing chess is between the person driving the bus and the person watching adventure movies##2
 5. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 6. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
 8. the person drinking milk is the person driving the tram##1
 9. the person driving the skateboard is in the middle##1
10. the person driving the bus is the person playing whist##1
11. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
12. the person playing whist is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
13. the person driving the tram is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
| Movie-Genre          | zombie  | animation     | adventure   | fantasy     | family |
| Beverage         | milk | water    | iced-tea  | lemonade | tea   |
| Transport   | tram        | helicopter    | skateboard     | motorbike     | bus    |
| Game   | snooker    | backgammon | mah-jongg | chess | whist   |

