5 different pets are kept: turtle, mouse, cat, lizard, goat
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: december, april, january, august, july
 1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
 2. the victorian house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 3. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 4. the person playing canasta is between the person who's birthday is in april and the cottage house##2
 5. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 6. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the victorian house##1
 7. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
 8. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 9. the person playing poker is on the far right##1
10. the person playing poker is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
11. the cottage house is on the left of the art-deco house##1
12. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
13. the art-deco house is on the right of the person playing chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |       2       |       3       |       4       |    5     |
