.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-17::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, chaman, oliveros, old-henry, montecristo
There 5 different types of food: pepper, kiwi, peach, pineapple, blueberry
There are 5 different nationalities: british, brazilian, thai, italian, canadian
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: september, march, january, may, july
 1. the canadian is between the person who's birthday is in march and the brazilian##2
 2. the thai is on the left of the italian##1
 3. the chaman-smoker is the person eating pineapple##1
 4. the havana-smoker is on the right of the canadian##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
 6. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 8. the person eating peach is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
 9. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person eating peach##1
10. the thai is on the far left##1
11. the person who's birthday is in january is between the thai and the person eating peach##2
12. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
13. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Cigar    | oliveros       | old-henry    | montecristo | chaman  | havana        |
| Food       | blueberry | pepper | peach  | pineapple | kiwi    |
| Nationality       | thai        | italian   | brazilian  | canadian   | british |
| Birthday   | may       | january      | july      | september | march  |

