.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, pall-mall, blend, baccarat, vegafina
The people use 5 different means of transport: car, ship, taxi, jet-ski, subway
5 different games are played: billiard, go, whist, domino, chess
There are 5 different favourite colors: coral, fuchsia, lilac, chestnut, aquamarine
 1. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person playing go##1
 2. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person playing whist and the person driving the taxi##2
 3. the baccarat-smoker is the person driving the jet-ski##1
 4. the person playing chess is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
 5. the person playing billiard is in the middle##1
 6. the baccarat-smoker is between the person driving the subway and the person who likes fuchsia##2
 7. the person who likes chestnut is the blend-smoker##1
 8. the dannemann-smoker is the person who likes lilac##1
 9. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
10. the person driving the car is on the right of the person playing whist##1
11. the person driving the taxi is the person playing go##1
12. the person playing domino is on the far left##1
13. the vegafina-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Cigar      | dannemann      | pall-mall         | baccarat      | blend | vegafina     |
| Transport           | ship | taxi | jet-ski | subway    | car  |
| Game   | domino  | go    | billiard | whist    | chess |
| Color   | lilac  | fuchsia        | coral   | chestnut    | aquamarine     |

