.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-19::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: juiced-games, surfing, tennis, water-polo, parkour
There 5 different types of food: pumpkin, cranberry, peas, orange, onion
House: futuristic, art-deco, farmhouse, cape-cod, townhouse
There are 5 different favourite beverages: cola, juice, 7up, almond-milk, fanta
 1. the townhouse house is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 2. the person eating orange is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
 3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 4. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
 5. the art-deco house is between the person eating pumpkin and the futuristic house##2
 6. the person eating pumpkin is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's sport is tennis is between the person drinking cola and the person who's sport is parkour##2
 8. the person who's sport is surfing is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person who's sport is juiced-games##2
 9. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person who's sport is juiced-games##1
10. the person who's sport is juiced-games is on the right of the person eating onion##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |     4      |     5      |
| Sport         | parkour  | tennis | water-polo   | surfing      | juiced-games |
| Food   | pumpkin   | orange    | cranberry | onion | peas      |
| House           | farmhouse | art-deco    | futuristic       | cape-cod     | townhouse      |
| Beverage     | 7up | fanta        | cola  | juice        | almond-milk    |

