.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-20::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  scientist, electrician, doctor, nurse, videographer
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: daisy, poppy, sunflower, azalea, dahlia
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: january, november, december, september, july
There are 5 different favourite beverages: water, almond-milk, lemonade, milk, mirinda
 1. the scientist is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
 2. the person who growsdahlia is between the person drinking milk and the person who's birthday is in july##2
 3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the videographer##1
 4. the person who growsdahlia is the person who's birthday is in january##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in january is between the person drinking mirinda and the person who's birthday is in december##2
 6. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the videographer##1
 7. the person who growssunflower is the person who's birthday is in september##1
 8. the nurse is the person who's birthday is in november##1
 9. the person drinking water is the person who's birthday is in november##1
10. the nurse is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
11. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the electrician##1
12. the person who growspoppy is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4       |       5       |
| Job         | doctor    | videographer  | electrician  | scientist      | nurse |
| Flower   | poppy    | dahlia   | azalea | sunflower | daisy   |
| Birthday   | december | january    | july    | september       | november         |
| Beverage   | milk  | almond-milk | mirinda    | lemonade     | water      |

 